  <h2>Towbars</h2>
  <p> Buchans for Towbars are the largest independent supplier and fitter of quality towbars to cars, vans, 4x4's and commercial vehicles in Scotland with depots in both Glasgow and Edinburgh. </p>
  <p> We offer a towbar fitting service as well as <a href="quotes.aspx" class="pl">mail order</a> from all of the industry&rsquo;s leading manufacturers. We stock numerous towing accessories along with over 1400 towbars from manufacturers such as Brink, 
  Bosal, PCT, Tow-Trust, Witter and Westfalia. </p>
  <p> Our fully trained and experienced fitters can fit your towbar, electrics and any towbar accessory efficiently and safely at our premises, alternatively we can supply instructions for DIY fitting. All towbars supplied and fitted come with a manufacturers' lifetime guarantee and comply with <a href="legislation.htm" class="pl">current legislation</a>. </p>
  <p><a href="http://www.brinkweb.com" target="_blank"><img src="../images/brink_Logo.gif" alt="Brink Towbars" width="160" height="50" hspace="10" vspace="10" border="0" align="right" /></a><a href="http://www.brinkweb.com" target="_blank" class="pl">Thule Towbars</a> are the largest manufacturer of towbars in the world. They develop original equipment towbars for the vast majority of vehicle manufacturers, offering a range of more than 1200 towbars to fit most makes and models of vehicle. </p>
  <p> The Thule name is permanently linked to quality, meeting all requirements presented by both official authorities and motor manufacturers. </p>
  <p><strong> Buchans for Towbars are proud to hold the sole distributorship for 
  Thule Towbars in Scotland. </strong> <a href="../company/contact.htm" class="pl">Trade enquiries</a> welcome.</p>
  <p> <a href="http://www.witter-towbars.co.uk/" target="_blank"><img src="../images/Witter_Logo.gif" alt="Witter Towbars" width="125" height="65" hspace="30" border="0" align="right" /></a><a href="http://www.witter-towbars.co.uk/" target="_blank" class="pl">Witter Towbars</a> are Britain's leading towbar manufacturer. Established in 1950 they are an independent company offering a range of over 800 towbars which cover the majority of vehicle makes and models. </p>
  <p> Witter provide all towbars with a genuine lifetime guarantee known as the Witter Shield of Safety.<a href="http://www.westfalia-automotive.de" target="_blank"><img class="auto-style1" height="61" src="../images/westfalia.gif" style="float: right" width="146" /></a></p>
